# Brand Images for HACS

This folder contains brand images for the Connee Alarm integration.

## Files
- **icon.png** - Integration icon (128x128 recommended)
- **icon@2x.png** - Retina integration icon (256x256)
- **logo.png** - Integration logo (256x256 recommended)
- **logo@2x.png** - Retina logo (512x512)

These images are used by HACS to display the integration in the list.
